                  <ead:physdesc>0.3 linear ft.</ead:physdesc>
               </ead:did>
               <ead:scopecontent>
                  <ead:p>The Activities series gives examples of the types of activities offered at the camp. The folders contain reports, schedules, and inventories from each activity area of the camp. These records are predominantly from the late 1960s and early 1970s and replicate some of the information found in the staff manuals.</ead:p>
               </ead:scopecontent>
               <ead:c02 level="file">
                  <ead:did>
                     <ead:container localtype="box">1</ead:container>
                     <ead:unittitle>General</ead:unittitle>
                     <ead:unitdate unitdatetype="inclusive">1970-1971</ead:unitdate>
                  </ead:did>
               </ead:c02>
               <ead:c02 level="file">
                  <ead:did>
